rvatskoj pomo\u0107 protiv koronavirusa|work=Glas Istre|date=9 April 2020|author=Hina|language=hr}}</ref>\n* {{Flag|United Arab Emirates}} has donated 11.5 tones of personal protective equipment.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.vecernji.hr/vijesti/stigla-donacija-od-115-tona-medicinske-opreme-od-vlade-uae-1387573|title=Stigla donacija 11,5 tona medicinske opreme od Vlade UAE|last=Rimac Lesi\u010dki|first=Ivana|date=30 March 2020|website=Ve\u010dernji list|language=hr|url-status=live|archive-url=|archive-date=|accessdate=31 March 2020}}</ref>\n* {{Flagdeco|United Nations}} [[UNICEF]] has donated 4.4 tones of personal protective equipment.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.vecernji.hr/vijesti/unicef-dostavio-cetiri-tone-zastitne-i-medicinske-opreme-u-hrvatsku-1390279|title=Iz Kopenhagen stigle \u010detiri tone medicinskih maski, rukavica, odijela...|last=Kova\u010devi\u0107|first=Radmila|date=30 March 2020|website=Ve\u010dernji list|language=hr|url-status=live|archive-url=|archive-date=|accessdate=31 March 2020}}</ref>\n\n== See also ==\n* [[2009 flu pandemic in Croatia]]\n* [[COVID-19 pandemic in Europe]]\n* [[COVID-19 pandemic in Austria]]\n* [[COVID-19 pandemic in Bosnia and Herzegovina]]\n* [[COVID-19 pandemic in Hungary]]\n* [[COVID-19 pandemic in Italy]]\n* [[COVID-19 pandemic in Kosovo]]\n* [[COVID-19 pandemic in Montenegro]]\n* [[COVID-19 pandemic in Serbia]]\n* [[COVID-19 pandemic in Slovenia]]\n* [[2020 Zagreb earthquake]]\n\n{{Portal bar|COVID-19|Croatia|Medicine|Viruses}}\n\n== Notes ==\n{{notelist}}\n\n== References ==\n{{reflist}}\n\n== External links ==\n* {{official|https://www.koronavirus.hr/}}\n* [https://civilna-zastita.gov.hr/ Ravnateljstvo civilne za\u0161tite]\n\n{{2019\u201320 coronavirus pandemic}}\n\n[[Category:Modern history of Croatia]]\n[[Category:2020 coronavirus pandemic in Croatia| ]]\n[[Category:2019\u201320 coronavirus pandemic by country|Croatia]]\n[[Category:2020 coronavirus pandemic in Europe|Croatia]]\n[[Category:2020 in Croatia|Corona